Package com.cy_siao.model

Class RestrictionType

java.lang.Object
com.cy_siao.model.RestrictionType
public class RestrictionType extends Object
Represents restriction rules applied to rooms (age and gender). This class defines restrictions for rooms based on age ranges and gender.
